4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to train students in essential technologies such as JavaScript and Python. The program spans 18 weeks, with 3 classes each week, maintaining a small class size of 1 instructor per 7 students. No prior coding skills are required, making it accessible to beginners. Students will learn to build websites, enhance their apps through APIs, and culminate their experience by developing a personal project. The bootcamp is available in both English and Spanish. Successful participants receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop